-Too busy.

09:54.595 --> 09:56.426
Tara call?

09:56.680 --> 10:00.593
Not yet. Probably still sleeping it off.

10:01.018 --> 10:05.352
I'll tell you what, I am sick and tired
of waiting around to get strangled.

10:05.773 --> 10:07.604
That's not gonna happen while I'm here.

10:07.775 --> 10:11.359
You can't spend 24 hours a day with me
for the rest of my life.

10:11.820 --> 10:13.196
Sure I can.

10:14.990 --> 10:18.198
I wanna find that guy
before he finds me again.

10:18.368 --> 10:21.280
So you're looking up killers
in the yellow pages?

10:21.455 --> 10:23.195
No.

10:23.916 --> 10:25.326
I remembered.

10:25.959 --> 10:28.371
In my sleep, I remembered.

10:29.254 --> 10:30.630
What?

10:31.548 --> 10:35.541
The girl I saw. Her clothes,
the apron, it was a uniform.

10:35.719 --> 10:38.586
She was a waitress and there was a tag.
Her name was Cindy.

10:38.764 --> 10:41.756
And the restaurant name
was something about pies.

10:41.934 --> 10:45.176
Party Pies or Patty Pies.

10:47.564 --> 10:50.351
-Wait, you mean Big Patty's Pie House?
-Yes.

10:50.526 --> 10:54.735
Well, yeah, I know Big Patty's.
lt's off l-49, a ways south, near Bunkie.

10:56.782 --> 10:59.068
You don't have to come with me.

11:00.327 --> 11:01.658
Yeah, I do.

11:01.829 --> 11:04.912
-Come on, eat up, you need your fuel.
-l'm not hungry.

11:05.082 --> 11:08.574
-Don't sass me.
-You're not the boss of me.

11:08.836 --> 11:12.670
-Oh, right, you are.
-Yeah.

11:18.470 --> 11:20.552
Hey, you. Going to work?

11:24.601 --> 11:26.592
Yeah, me too in a second.

11:27.729 --> 11:30.766
Look, I wanted to say I'm really sorry.

11:33.318 --> 11:36.606
We are done with this shit,
do you hear me? Done.

11:37.155 --> 11:38.816
I want every drop out of my house.

11:38.991 --> 11:43.030
And if you don't like it,
you can pack your goddamn bags and go.

11:53.589 --> 11:54.954
Love you.

11:55.132 --> 11:57.123
We caught up with
Senator David Finch...

11:57.301 --> 12:00.634
...speaking to the Marthavi/Ie Order
of Visionary Southern Gentlemen...

12:00.804 --> 12:04.467
...as he embarks on his campaign
for the U. 8. House of Representatives.

12:04.641 --> 12:09.635
