-He has what? He didn't tell me that.

12:09.813 --> 12:12.646
Equal rights for vampires?
I don’t think so.

12:13.817 --> 12:16.229
-Many of them are foreign immigrants.
-What the fuck?

12:16.403 --> 12:19.270
Taking our jobs and our women.

12:19.615 --> 12:22.903
And their very blood turns our children...

12:23.076 --> 12:27.240
...into addicts, drug dealers
and homosexuals. No vampire...

12:27.414 --> 12:30.952
...and none of these vampire-loving
deviants deserve any rights at all.

12:31.126 --> 12:33.412
You's a lying-ass motherfucker.

12:33.587 --> 12:36.670
-Two-faced son of a bitch.
-...managed his family’s hardware store.

12:36.840 --> 12:40.674
-Did you hear what he just said?
