12:55.984 --> 12:59.522
Oh, darling, you looking a little used up.

13:00.030 --> 13:01.986
Jason dragging you into his bullshit?

13:03.700 --> 13:06.237
l have no idea what you mean.

13:06.995 --> 13:09.031
-Right inside.
-Terry?

13:09.206 --> 13:10.787
Yeah.

13:11.083 --> 13:14.826
-Why is everybody telling me lies today?
-I got no idea.

13:15.003 --> 13:19.667
-Look at that, Lafayette, theme shelves.
-Oh, that's pretty, baby.

13:20.217 --> 13:22.629
Would you work for me tonight?

13:24.096 --> 13:27.213
No, ma'am, no, sir.
I don't know any Cindy.

13:27.391 --> 13:31.225
