the chess pie, the seven-layer Jell-O pie.

13:36.233 --> 13:41.444
They'll have the peanut butter pie and
the Spunky Hollow honey pineapple pie.

13:41.613 --> 13:43.729
-Please, Harley.
-Gotcha, Buster.

13:43.907 --> 13:46.899
-We will?
-You won't get nothing from her.

13:47.077 --> 13:49.693
She's only been here two weeks.

13:50.163 --> 13:52.415
Comes from three generations
of dumb as rocks.

13:52.582 --> 13:56.575
-Hell, they named her after a motorcycle.
-That's real interesting, but--

13:56.753 --> 14:00.211
If you wanna know anything
about Cindy Marshall, I'll talk to you.

14:00.382 --> 14:03.749
And I'll eat that pie too. Buster Boisseau.

14:03.927 --> 14:06.589
Sookie Stackhouse, Sam Merlotte.

14:06.763 --> 14:10.381
-Yeah. Can you tell us--?
-First things first.

14:12.477 --> 14:16.265
-You knew Cindy?
-A little bit.

14:16.440 --> 14:21.685
Let's see, I met her two years ago.
She moved into town with her brother...

14:21.862 --> 14:24.274
...a couple of months before....

14:25.615 --> 14:26.900
Before what?

14:28.118 --> 14:32.361
Well, I hate to be the one to tell you,
but somebody murdered that little gal.

14:32.956 --> 14:35.868
-Just choked the life right out of her.
-Poor thing.

14:36.043 --> 14:39.410
-Did they find out who did it?
-Nope. It's a mystery.

14:39.588 --> 14:43.331
-Where's her brother? Could we talk to him?
-Don't know how.

14:43.508 --> 14:46.215
He was gone
by the time they found her body.

14:46.386 --> 14:49.628
The police thought maybe he's dead too
or maybe he killed her.

14:49.806 --> 14:52.593
But there wasn't no evidence
one way or the other.

14:54.644 --> 14:57.477
-What was his name?
-Let me think on that.

14:58.190 --> 15:00.351
Nobody hardly knew him.

15:00.525 --> 15:05.360
Let's see, D something. Dave.

15:05.530 --> 15:07.111
Drew. No, Drew. Drew Marshall.

15:08.533 --> 15:13.197
-What was Cindy like?
-Oh, cute as a button, a little wild...

15:13.371 --> 15:16.499
...fun-loving, always nice to me.

15:17.000 --> 15:19.286
But people talked, you know.

15:20.170 --> 15:21.660
Talked about what?

15:23.590 --> 15:24.955
Vampires.

15:25.133 --> 15:28.751
They say she was carrying on
with the vampires. I didn't believe her.

15:28.929 --> 15:31.887
