always do, I'll just go for a little walk.

16:35.871 --> 16:38.237
Well, that's just plain sad.

16:39.249 --> 16:41.581
lt's you and me, brother.

16:41.751 --> 16:44.584
We'll play some pool,
I'll buy you a po'boy.

16:44.754 --> 16:48.246
