-You won't.

16:51.094 --> 16:53.676
It's a date, I said. Me and my woman.

16:54.181 --> 16:56.388
All right, fine.

16:56.558 --> 16:59.174
Fuck it. I'll party on my own.

16:59.352 --> 17:02.719
What do you want with us when you got
Amy? God, she's good-looking.

17:07.360 --> 17:11.444
Well, I'm gonna tell you something,
but you can't say nothing to nobody.

17:11.615 --> 17:13.571
You got that?

17:16.703 --> 17:18.694
Amy likes V.

