18:17.639 --> 18:19.675
Yeah, that makes sense.

18:20.350 --> 18:22.591
-Thanks.
-Okay.

18:23.770 --> 18:26.807
-Hang in there, bro.
-All right.

18:27.732 --> 18:30.940
Okay. These things, they got
a way of working out, you know?

18:31.111 --> 18:32.817
I hope you're right.

18:32.988 --> 18:36.321
-All right. Night.
-Night.

